LA HABRA SHOOTING CRITICALLY INJURES MAN 
A man was in critical condition Saturday evening, suffering from gunshot wounds 
in what police said appeared to be a gang-related shooting in the 700 block of 
West 4th Avenue in La Habra. 
The unidentified man was taken to a Whittier hospital. 
A suspect in the shooting apparently entered a nearby house at 4th Street and 
Monte Vista Avenue. 
A special police team surrounded the house. 
